---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About PackagingConveyor.com | The Packaging Conveyor Resource"
  description="PackagingConveyor.com is an independent technical resource for packaging conveyor systems. Learn about our editorial approach and how we research our guides."
  canonical="https://packagingconveyor.com/about/"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-surface-dim bg-dots">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="section-label text-accent mb-4">The Resource</div>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-800 text-ink tracking-wide uppercase leading-tight mb-6">
        About This Resource
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-ink-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        An independent technical reference for engineers and managers who specify packaging conveyor systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What is PackagingConveyor.com -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="section-label text-accent mb-4">What This Site Is</div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-800 text-ink tracking-wide mb-8">
        What is PackagingConveyor.com?
      </h2>
      <div class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-ink">PackagingConveyor.com is not a manufacturer. It is not a distributor.</strong> We do not sell equipment, take commissions, or represent any conveyor brand.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is an independent editorial resource — vendor-neutral technical guides built for plant engineers, packaging managers, and capital project teams who need real data to spec conveyor systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          We cover <strong class="text-ink">30+ conveyor types</strong> across food and beverage, pharmaceutical, automotive, and warehouse applications. Every guide includes real pricing ranges, engineering specifications, and honest selection criteria — the kind of information you need before you issue an RFQ.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Editorial Approach -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-surface-dim bg-dots">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="section-label text-accent mb-4">How We Work</div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-800 text-ink tracking-wide mb-8">
        Our Editorial Approach
      </h2>
      <div class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          Content on this site is researched from manufacturer specification sheets, CEMA (Conveyor Equipment Manufacturers Association) standards, industry trade publications, and direct industry experience in packaging line design.
        </p>
        <p>
          Pricing ranges are verified across multiple vendors and configurations. We update data when market conditions shift. We do not rely on a single manufacturer's published list price.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-ink">We do not accept payment for coverage, rankings, or recommendations.</strong> If a conveyor type is covered here, it's because it's relevant — not because a manufacturer paid to be included.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Site Exists -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="section-label text-accent mb-4">The Problem We Solve</div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-800 text-ink tracking-wide mb-8">
        Why This Site Exists
      </h2>
      <div class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          Manufacturer websites show you their products. Distributor catalogs lack engineering context. Most of the remaining web content on conveyor systems is thin SEO filler with no real specifications.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you've ever tried to build a conveyor budget or write a spec sheet from scratch, you already know the problem. The information you need — actual price ranges, throughput formulas, comparison criteria between types — isn't easy to find in one place.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-ink">We built the resource that plant engineers and packaging managers actually need to spec a system.</strong> Use it to build your shortlist, define your requirements, and write an RFQ you can send to any vendor.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-surface-dim bg-dots">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="section-label text-accent mb-4">Contact</div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-800 text-ink tracking-wide mb-8">
        Get in Touch
      </h2>
      <div class="text-lg text-ink-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          For editorial inquiries, corrections, or content feedback, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@packagingconveyor.com" class="text-accent font-semibold hover:text-accent-hover">info@packagingconveyor.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          We do not field quote requests or supplier referrals through this address.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
